org.trimou.engine.listener

Class EnhancedStatsCollector

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.trimou.engine.config.AbstractConfigurationAware
      • org.trimou.engine.listener.AbstractMustacheListener
        • org.trimou.engine.listener.AbstractStatsCollector
          • org.trimou.engine.listener.EnhancedStatsCollector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ConfigurationAware, MustacheListener

    public class EnhancedStatsCollector
extends AbstractStatsCollector
    Unlike SimpleStatsCollector this listener is able to detect rendering errors. Also Identified.getGeneratedId() is used to map statistics to a template. On the other hand it's more resource-intensive.
    Author:
    Martin Kouba
